<concept id="concept_ocm_bzq_m3c">
    <title>4. Security Model</title>
    <conbody>
        <section id="section_v4d_czq_m3c">
            <title>API Key Management</title>
            <p>LLM API keys must be stored only within the serverless platform.</p>
            <p>They must <b>never appear in client-side code</b>.</p>
        </section>
        <section id="section_w4d_czq_m3c">
            <title>Access Control</title>
            <p>CORS should restrict requests to:</p>
            <pre>portfolio domain</pre>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
